content.raw:
Oh, I think the plotting branch is not synced with default yet, so your branch ended up ahead of plotting, thus the huge diff. Plus, it looks like some conflicts weren't resolved properly, so your branch is not compiling.

I don't think there is an easy way of restoring things now. I think the solution would be to start a new branch from the latest plotting branch and make a new PR. Sorry for the extra trouble.
